## TC-LOGIN-001: Successful login with standard_user

> **Why this TC?**
> This is the most critical test in the entire application — the "happy path".
> If standard_user cannot log in, all remaining tests are blocked.
> Always execute this TC first before any other test case.

| Field | Details |
|-------|---------|
| **ID** | TC-LOGIN-001 |
| **Module** | Login |
| **Priority** | 🔴 High |
| **Type** | Positive / Functional / Smoke |
| **Preconditions** | Browser open, navigate to https://www.saucedemo.com |
| **Test Data** | Username: `standard_user` / Password: `secret_sauce` |

**Steps:**
1. Open https://www.saucedemo.com
2. Verify the login form is visible (username field, password field, Login button)
3. Enter `standard_user` in the Username field
4. Enter `secret_sauce` in the Password field
5. Click the **LOGIN** button

**Expected Result:**
- User is redirected to `/inventory.html`
- Page header shows **"Swag Labs"**
- 6 products are visible on the page
- Shopping cart icon is visible in the top right corner

**Actual Result:** _(fill during execution)_
**Status:** ⬜ Not Executed
**Notes:** This is a Smoke Test — run this first before any other TC
**JIRA:** EPIC-01 / TC-LOGIN-001

