## Negative Test Cases (TC-LOGIN-007 to TC-LOGIN-012)

> **Group goal:** Check that the application stops wrong login attempts
> and shows clear error messages to the user.
> Tests check empty fields, wrong username or password, and a simple
> security test (SQL Injection) to make sure the application is safe.

